ActAn Act to amend the Divorce Act, the Family Orders and Agreements Enforcement Assistance Act and the Garnishment, Attachment and Pension Diversion Act and to make consequential amendments to another Act
SubjectOrder Fixing July 1, 2020 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing July 1, 2020 as the day on which subsections 1(1) to (4), (6) and (7), sections 2 to 6 and 8 to 15, subsection 16(2), sections 17 to 19, 21, 22 and 23 to 25, subsection 28(3) and sections 32 to 35 of AN ACT TO AMEND THE DIVORCE ACT, THE FAMILY ORDERS AND AGREEMENTS ENFORCEMENT ASSISTANCE ACT AND THE GARNISHMENT, ATTACHEMENT AND PENSION DIVERSION ACT AND TO MAKE CONSEQUENTIAL AMENDMENTS TO ANOTHER ACT, chapter 16 of the Statutes of Canada, 2019, COME INTO FORCE.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2019-0082 Publication Date: 2019-08-21
AttachmentsAttachment
